Connect With Us

Join an action network of Americans who advocate for federal public media funding!

Without federal funding many stations would cease to exist, meaning the end to critical local news, culture, history, and emergency communications.

Take a stand for the WKNO and the programs you love.

Hello, Mr. Chuck! is an educational children’s show that deals with values, conflict resolution and things children struggle with.

Episodes to be released on the 1st and 15th of each month.

Why donate your vehicle to WKNO?

WKNO-TV uses the power of non-commercial public broadcasting to provide the Mid-South with quality educational and cultural programs.

Invest in your community by donating your car to WKNO-TV. We accept all types of vehicles - including SUVs, trucks, RVs, jet skis, and even boats!
